# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:18
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_fa520e80:

    # "As we work on our assignments in English class, Mrs. McGee comes by my desk and leans down to whisper in my ear."
    "Mientras trabajamos en nuestras tareas en la clase de inglés, la Sra. McGee se acerca a mi pupitre y se inclina para susurrarme al oído."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:19
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_d9b1882f:

    # et "[pcname], would you stay after class a few moments. There's something I'd like to discuss with you."
    et "[pcname], ¿te quedarías un rato después de clase? Hay algo de lo que me gustaría hablar contigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:20
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:23
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_cc0f4023:

    # "Wonder what she could want to talk about this time? Whatever it is, I'm excited to find out."
    "Me pregunto de qué querrá hablar esta vez. Sea lo que sea, estoy deseando averiguarlo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:26
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_6facc3ac:

    # "After the rest of the classroom empties, Mrs. McGee shuts the door and sits on her desk."
    "Cuando el resto de la clase se ha ido, la Sra. McGee cierra la puerta y se sienta en su escritorio."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:27
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_1e1882e3:

    # et "Would you like to come over to my house for dinner tonight?"
    et "¿Te gustaría venir a cenar a mi casa esta noche?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:28
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_9bc190a8:

    # pc "Dinner?"
    pc "¿A cenar?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:29
translate spanish mrsmcgee10a_d5ef02f0:

    # et "Yes, if you'd like. I make a very nice kasha. I promise you will have a good time."
    et "Sí, si te apetece. Hago un kasha muy bueno. Te prometo que lo pasarás bien."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:34
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_ececefc2:

    # et "Good, then I will see you this evening. Say, around 6:30?"
    et "Bien, entonces nos vemos esta tarde. ¿Digamos, sobre las 6:30?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:35
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_36ffe6b6:

    # "She hands me a note with her address on it."
    "Me entrega una nota con su dirección."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:36
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_ad15b3ba:

    # pc "I'll be there. Should I bring anything?"
    pc "Allí estaré. ¿Debo llevar algo?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:37
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_4ee87fdf:

    # et "Just you. That's all I need."
    et "Solo a ti. Es todo lo que necesito."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:38
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_696181f3:

    # pc "Okay then, see you tonight."
    pc "De acuerdo, entonces, nos vemos esta noche."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:39
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_dd6a1a96:

    # et "Goodbye, [pcname]."
    et "Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:43
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_3f5db218:

    # "I leave her class, looking forward to whatever is going to happen tonight. It definitely seems like she wants more than to just eat dinner with me."
    "Salgo de su clase, deseando saber qué va a pasar esta noche. Definitivamente parece que ella quiere algo más que simplemente cenar conmigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:44
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_dc3258ef:

    # "And I want more than that with her too."
    "Y yo también quiero algo más que eso con ella."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:51
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_eea40836:

    # et "Oh. Maybe some other time then."
    et "Oh. Quizás en otra ocasión, entonces."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:52
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:53
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_577e28d7:

    # et "Have a good day, [pcname]."
    et "Que tengas un buen día, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:54
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_eb61ef6e:

    # pc "You too."
    pc "Tú también."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:57
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_b142bee1:

    # "I leave and go on with the rest of my day. I wonder why I turned that down? Maybe I'm not really interested in Mrs. McGee at all."
    "Me voy y sigo con el resto de mi día. Me pregunto por qué lo rechacé. Quizás no me interesa en absoluto la Sra. McGee."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:63
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_d4a7d900:

    # et "Oh, it's a type of soup or porridge, with cereal in it."
    et "Oh, es una especie de sopa o gachas, con cereales."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:64
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_3d903830:

    # pc "Like Frosted Flakes or something?"
    pc "¿Como Frosted Flakes o algo así?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:65
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_230a666c:

    # et "Um, no... not like Frosted Flakes."
    et "Eh, no... no como los Frosted Flakes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:66
translate spanish mrsmcgee10menu_a3518e13:

    # et "It's good. You will like it. So what do you think? Will you come?"
    et "Está bueno. Te va a gustar. ¿Qué te parece? ¿Vas a venir?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:76
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_a5aa248c:

    # "After I leave work, I drive home, take a quick shower, and change clothes, then head over to the address that Mrs. McGee gave me."
    "Después de salir del trabajo, conduzco a casa, me doy una ducha rápida y me cambio de ropa, y luego me dirijo a la dirección que me dio la señora McGee."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:79
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_c2171e40:

    # "I pull up into the driveway and park. She lives in a small house in the suburbs, much like my own."
    "Entro en el camino de acceso y aparco. Vive en una casita en las afueras, muy parecida a la mía."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:80
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_c58d627f:

    # "A little nervous about how things are going to go tonight, I take a deep breath, then step out and walk up to the door."
    "Un poco nerviosa por cómo van a ir las cosas esta noche, respiro hondo, salgo del coche y me acerco a la puerta."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:83
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_0b66d801:

    # "When I get to the door, I raise my hand to knock..."
    "Cuando llego a la puerta, levanto la mano para llamar..."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:85
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_0a429c3d:

    # "But before my knuckles touch wood, the door swings open and Mr. McGee is standing there with a big smile on his face."
    "Pero antes de que mis nudillos toquen la madera, la puerta se abre de par en par y el Sr. McGee está allí de pie con una gran sonrisa en la cara."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:86
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_bda45b99:

    # mrmg "[pcname]! I'm so glad you came! Come on in!"
    mrmg "¡Me alegro mucho de que hayas venido! ¡Pasa, pasa!"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:89
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_f8f82946:

    # "I walk in and stand in the foyer, a little awkward. The place smells amazing - that savory smell of grilled onions with an underhint of bacon."
    "Entro y me quedo en el vestíbulo, un poco incómoda. La casa huele de maravilla: ese aroma apetitoso a cebollas asadas con un ligero toque a beicon."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:90
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_fb665e30:

    # pc "Thank you for inviting me, Mr. McGee."
    pc "Gracias por invitarme, Sr. McGee."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:91
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_5ba2ce58:

    # mrmg "Oh that's going to be weird if you keep calling me Mister. Call me Pete, okay?"
    mrmg "Oh, va a ser raro si sigues llamándome «señor». Llámame Pete, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:92
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_845da3d6:

    # pc "Alright, Pete."
    pc "De acuerdo, Pete."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:94
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_3561000e:

    # mrmg "I think Edie's done cooking and is in the bedroom getting dressed now, if you want to join me in the dining room, we can wait for her there."
    mrmg "Creo que Edie ya ha terminado de cocinar y ahora está en el dormitorio vistiéndose; si quieres acompañarme al comedor, podemos esperarla allí."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:95
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_74dad17c:

    # pc "Okay, sure."
    pc "Vale, claro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:98
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_ce18fa39:

    # mrmg "Are you okay? You seem a little nervous."
    mrmg "¿Estás bien? Pareces un poco nerviosa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:99
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_4c567549:

    # pc "I am... this is a little weird."
    pc "Lo estoy... esto es un poco raro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:100
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_f000a834:

    # mrmg "It's fine, I promise. We both like you and just wanted to have dinner and talk a bit."
    mrmg "No pasa nada, te lo prometo. A los dos nos caes bien y solo queríamos cenar y charlar un rato."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:101
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_760593d6:

    # mrmg "And we'll just leave it at that if you don't want to take it any further."
    mrmg "Y lo dejaremos ahí si no quieres ir más allá."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:102
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_67b4f891:

    # mrmg "At the very least, you'll get some good food. Edie's kasha is amazing."
    mrmg "Como mínimo, disfrutarás de una buena comida. El kasha de Edie está increíble."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:103
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_8e1808a3:

    # pc "Mrs. McGee's name is Edie?"
    pc "¿La señora McGee se llama Edie?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:104
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_6ed863ba:

    # mrmg "Well, Eden. But I call her Edie."
    mrmg "Bueno, Eden. Pero yo la llamo Edie."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:107
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_3ea2e3a2:

    # mrmg "There she is, my beautiful wife."
    mrmg "Ahí está, mi preciosa esposa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:108
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_ce59dba2:

    # pc "Wow."
    pc "Vaya."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:109
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_6c592216:

    # et "Hello, boys. Hitting it off in here?"
    et "Hola, chicos. ¿Os estáis llevando bien por aquí?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:110
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_11adb751:

    # mrmg "We were just talking about you."
    mrmg "Justo estábamos hablando de ti."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:111
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_0b1aa19c:

    # et "Oh yeah? I like that."
    et "¿Ah, sí? Me gusta eso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:112
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_fb640479:

    # et "I'm glad you made it, [pcname]."
    et "Me alegro de que hayáis venido, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:113
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_c8e5d523:

    # et "Are you two ready to eat?"
    et "¿Estáis listos para comer?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:114
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_e9a44191:

    # mrmg "Absolutely. I'm starving."
    mrmg "Por supuesto. Me muero de hambre."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:117
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_99840180:

    # "She serves the kasha to us, putting a glass of white wine along with the bowls. Then she surprises me by sitting next to me instead of her husband."
    "Nos sirve el kasha y pone una copa de vino blanco junto a los cuencos. Luego me sorprende sentándose a mi lado en lugar de junto a su marido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:118
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_1c875ad0:

    # et "I hope you enjoy. Kasha is one of my specialties."
    et "Espero que lo disfrutéis. El kasha es una de mis especialidades."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:119
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_d21d1a56:

    # pc "It smells delicious."
    pc "Huele delicioso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:122
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_938106e2:

    # "I spoon a bite into my mouth, then a few more spoonfuls as well."
    "Me llevo una cucharada a la boca, y luego unas cuantas más."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:123
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_57c039b1:

    # pc "Tastes delicious too. Wow, that's good."
    pc "También sabe delicioso. Vaya, qué bueno está."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:124
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_c688553f:

    # et "I'm so glad you like it."
    et "Me alegro mucho de que te guste."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:125
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_021eca64:

    # mrmg "I've never met anybody who didn't love Edie's cooking. It's one of the many things that she's incredible at."
    mrmg "Nunca he conocido a nadie a quien no le encante la cocina de Edie. Es una de las muchas cosas en las que es increíble."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:126
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_43260e5f:

    # et "You're going to make me blush, honey."
    et "Me vas a hacer sonrojar, cariño."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:127
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_da04860f:

    # mrmg "That's okay. You're gorgeous when you blush."
    mrmg "No pasa nada. Estás preciosa cuando te sonrojas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:130
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_2e788e2b:

    # mrmg "So, [pcname], we'd love to learn a bit more about you. Do you live with your parents?"
    mrmg "Bueno, [pcname], nos encantaría saber un poco más sobre ti. ¿Vives con tus padres?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:131
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_9f71a1fe:

    # "I spent the next few minutes telling them about my mom's death and my dad going missing, and Lisa and Suzy."
    "Pasé los siguientes minutos contándoles sobre la muerte de mi madre y la desaparición de mi padre, y sobre Lisa y Suzy."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:134
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_52df5a2c:

    # et "I had no idea you were going through all this. And you're still making straight A's in my class."
    et "No tenía ni idea de que estuvieras pasando por todo esto. Y sigues sacando sobresalientes en mi clase."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:135
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_6959b302:

    # et "I'm sorry you're having to deal with those things. It sounds like a hard situation."
    et "Siento que tengas que lidiar con esas cosas. Parece una situación difícil."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:136
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_4f633b03:

    # pc "It is, sometimes. But things haven't been all bad. This dinner, for instance."
    pc "Lo es, a veces. Pero no todo ha sido malo. Esta cena, por ejemplo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:137
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_a831879f:

    # et "I'm glad that I could make you feel a little better."
    et "Me alegro de haberte hecho sentir un poco mejor."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:140
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_1dd2ecf3:

    # mrmg "Do you have a girlfriend, [pcname]?"
    mrmg "¿Tienes novia, [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:143
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_ea5b0c28:

    # pc "Yeah, I do."
    pc "Sí, tengo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:144
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_5474e481:

    # mrmg "Are things serious?"
    mrmg "¿Va en serio?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:145
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_e01ed414:

    # pc "Pretty serious."
    pc "Bastante en serio."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:146
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_ce8a6513:

    # mrmg "I see."
    mrmg "Ya veo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:149
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_7e1bf495:

    # mrmg "Wow, that's hard to believe!"
    mrmg "¡Vaya, me cuesta creerlo!"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:150
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_9d64452a:

    # pc "You think so?"
    pc "¿Tú crees?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:151
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_e1f479aa:

    # mrmg "I mean, you're kind of a stud! I figured you'd be drowning in college girls."
    mrmg "¡Es que eres todo un semental! Pensaba que estarías rodeado de universitarias."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:152
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_29fc5af6:

    # pc "Yeah, not so much."
    pc "Sí, pero no tanto."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:153
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_f29811da:

    # mrmg "Well, you definitely caught Edie's attention at least."
    mrmg "Bueno, al menos has llamado la atención de Edie."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:155
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_d867934a:

    # mrmg "Ha! That's what I figured."
    mrmg "¡Ja! Eso es lo que me imaginaba."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:156
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_c7cf6fcb:

    # mrmg "You're kind of a stud! I knew you'd be drowning in college girls."
    mrmg "¡Eres todo un semental! Sabía que estarías rodeado de universitarias."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:157
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_64d17d06:

    # mrmg "You definitely caught Edie's attention."
    mrmg "Definitivamente has llamado la atención de Edie."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:160
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_6ef17689:

    # "We chit chat a bit more while we finish our bowls. I eat every last drop."
    "Charlamos un rato más mientras terminamos nuestros platos. Me como hasta la última gota."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:161
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_668c4331:

    # et "Did you get enough, dear?"
    et "¿Has comido suficiente, cariño?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:162
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_b4599cf5:

    # "It takes me a moment to realize that she's asking me, not her husband."
    "Tardo un momento en darme cuenta de que me lo está preguntando a mí, no a su marido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:163
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_b4bade14:

    # pc "Oh yes, Mrs. McGee, thank you."
    pc "Oh, sí, señora McGee, gracias."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:164
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_9d8d8515:

    # et "Call me Eden, please."
    et "Llámame Eden, por favor."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:165
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_180bb07c:

    # pc "Okay, Eden."
    pc "Vale, Eden."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:170
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_76f15013:

    # mrmg "I guess we should talk about the second reason we invited you over tonight, besides the food."
    mrmg "Supongo que deberíamos hablar de la segunda razón por la que te hemos invitado esta noche, además de la comida."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:171
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_e18be8a3:

    # mrmg "My wife likes you, [pcname]. Since the beginning of the school year, you're all she talks about."
    mrmg "A mi mujer le gustas, [pcname]. Desde que empezó el curso, no habla de otra cosa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:172
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_b3c66524:

    # mrmg "She lies in bed at night and tells me how much she wants to have sex with you."
    mrmg "Se acuesta por la noche y me cuenta lo mucho que quiere acostarse contigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:175
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_399bdc0f:

    # pc "Really?"
    pc "¿En serio?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:176
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_9880f614:

    # et "Yes."
    et "Sí."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:179
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_546d48e6:

    # mrmg "My wife and I love each other very much. We are extremely happy in our relationship."
    mrmg "Mi mujer y yo nos queremos mucho. Somos muy felices en nuestra relación."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:180
translate spanish mrsmcgee10_b6a18a9f:

    # mrmg "But she has a quite insatiable sexual appetite that sometimes I am unable to fill."
    mrmg "Pero ella tiene un apetito sexual bastante insaciable que a veces no soy capaz de satisfacer."

